 Section two describes the characteristics of the datasets employed in this
 research.
 It establishes key definitions and describes the study methods including
 the statistical analysis.
 Section three presents the comparison between bushfires and heatwaves in
 Victoria.
 Finally, section four presents a discussion of the results and conclusions.
 
\end_layout

